{"tid":190533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大要求取消民族黨產品寄賣活動　學生會斥校方政治打壓","createTime":"2017-04-07T07:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T01:29:15.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc0c48e702a01faa31b92e30dba95be2afcb4a2","tid":190533,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/04/city-u-students-union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F04%2Fcity-u-students-union%2F&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGogdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8b85f543\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/04/city-u-students-union/</a><br />\n<br />\n城市大學學生會昨日（六日）在facebook指，收到校方通知，以校園內不得進行商業活動為由，要求學生會取消前日起開始的民族黨產品寄賣活動。學生會以「政治打壓直逼校園，強烈譴責城大校方干涉學生會自主」為題發文指，會繼續寄賣活動至原訂的六月三十日，並強烈譴責校方粗暴干涉學生會自主，強調定必全力捍衛學生會自主、言論及思想自由。<br />\n<br />\n學生會指，已按該會評議會、財務委員會以及會章提供的指引填寫、核實、提交文件，在前天開始民族黨產品寄賣活動，但校方以「商業活動」為由，要求停止於學生會辦公室寄賣一律產品，即使幹事提出改在該會的合作社CUT PRICE繼續寄賣，校方又指合作社性質為「學生福利」，並不能涉及商業性質。<br />\n<br />\n學生會表示，若按此理由，校方理應取消所有於合作社的城市大學紀念品，認為校方唯獨打算取消民族黨的寄賣產品，「顯然易見此舉為活生生的政治打壓」。學生會指，不會因校方打壓而卑躬屈膝，會繼續寄賣活動至六月底，並「強烈譴責校方蓄意取消本會具合法性的寄賣活動，粗暴干涉學生會自主，並強調本會定必全力捍衛學生會自主、言論及思想自由。」<br />\n<br />\n民族黨原本在今年維園年宵投得攤檔，但臨時被食環署以「香港民族黨主張港獨，可能危害公共秩序」而取消攤檔特許經營資格。民族黨的年宵貨品之後曾分別在浸大學生會、港大學生會社會科學學會政治及公共行政學會、中大學生會協助下寄賣產品。"},{"pid":"3f24f4ecba12d5d884f4052c725aeaf5d9c6287b","tid":190533,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38557a33690cd281bcae8ed331b6a1b4f6eb91ec","tid":190533,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a5350b31b476d274cf6d5e08bc91cf43cc7ac0","tid":190533,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b4aa30262d58fa147205dafdeaadd9cbfc2cdb","tid":190533,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"又唔見泛民賣野比人打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己反省下啦，港獨ff撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb3b4637c510b4c2de0d131993700b2b5b1ef8f","tid":190533,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82910b24b643f66ff0e4729afd01b5db53efeff1","tid":190533,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a50ab14d23204ba9fd8a884d3fc9af6544ab71","tid":190533,"uid":56998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔見泛民賣野比人打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己反省下啦，港獨ff撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5毛出沒注意"},{"pid":"8f99d252dde73b7a74de643b2a0d04b969299ba1","tid":190533,"uid":44537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又唔見泛民賣野比人打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己反省下啦，港獨ff撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5毛出沒注意</blockquote><br />\nBlock左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4968ab5e45c0ea46b91f556469e728bc759f2b86","tid":190533,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"泛民係自己人，邊會去搞佢地<i